reviews.reviewbody: I have *not* DL'ed the .epub file yet, so I cannot attest to it's version only the online one ok? Anyway as far as I have read online, this title is awesome. The family reacts as real people would react in the same situation, for instance praying to God really hard and desperately in the face of impending doom. The content is SO well written. It is not "baby-ish", not the way a TV show for children today would be, it is a gripping and very interesting story that makes you eager to get to the next page.
